00:50.680 --> 00:59.860
water simply turned black. And I was up there looking at that, and I thought,
I'm like, God, you can't even tell. That's it, it looks like a gigantic hole in

00:59.860 --> 01:10.060
the ground. And immediately I thought, what would a city be like that would be
built around a gigantic shaft into the earth like that? What effect might that

01:10.060 --> 01:22.600
kind of physical environment have on the psychology of the people who lived in
that city, which is how the whole symbolism of, the religious symbolism of the

01:22.600 --> 01:32.740
city of Sur came to me. yeah good I was glad to get that every once in a while
