03:02.220 --> 03:11.880
our myths. And I suddenly just, there was a little click that goes on in your
head and I turned that around and said, well, I'd like you to think and write

03:11.880 --> 03:20.320
about aliens, and it's very difficult to write about an alien to the inside,
because I personally believe that aliens are inexplicable to us, that we're

03:20.320 --> 03:32.060
never going to understand them fully. So I thought possibly a good way of
dealing with the portrayal of an alien or an entire alien race would be to do it

03:32.060 --> 03:41.980
circuitously by telling an alien myth. And that is exactly what an answer to the
changer in the three years, of course, is an alien myth. And the myth itself is

03:41.980 --> 03:52.060
supposed to tell you a lot about the psychology of the race. Yeah, when I read
that, I got the impression that one of the points of it was that aliens are

03:52.060 --> 04:01.740
