12:10.500 --> 12:18.560
writing it, I don't think that people should approach the writing of science
fiction as anything other than simply writing a story, which happens to be

12:18.560 --> 12:26.680
science fiction. I think they should be aware, however, of what's done in
science fiction before so they don't repeat everything. It really gets

12:26.680 --> 12:37.660
embarrassing when you see a very good writer who hasn't worked in science
